				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You must be misreading the <a href="http://nesdevwiki.org/wiki/index.php/MMC1" class="postlink">wiki page</a>. It states that ORing with $0C affects only the PRG bank mode ($08) and PRG bank location ($04), <em>not</em> the CHR bank mode ($10) or the mirroring mode ($03).
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">4bit0<br />-----<br />CPRMM<br />|||||<br />|||++- Mirroring &#40;0: one-screen, lower bank; 1: one-screen, upper bank;<br />|||&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2: vertical; 3: horizontal&#41;<br />||+--- PRG ROM bank location &#40;0: switch 16 KB at $C000; 1: switch 16 KB at $8000<br />||&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; only used when PRG bank mode bit below is set to 1&#41;<br />|+---- PRG ROM bank mode &#40;0: switch 32 KB at $8000, ignoring low bit of bank number;<br />|&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1: switch 16 KB at address specified by location bit above&#41;<br />+----- CHR ROM bank mode &#40;0: switch 8 KB at a time; 1: switch two separate 4 KB banks&#41;</div></div>

					
							<br /><br />
							<span class="gensmall">Last edited by <a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9" style="color: #AA0000;" class="username-coloured">tepples</a> on Sun Nov 04, 2007 4:09 pm, edited 1 time in total.</span>
